<br><br><br><div><span class="floatRightHeader"><a href="/anime/2694/Hidamari_no_Ki/reviews">More reviews</a></span><h2>Reviews</h2></div>
              
<div class="borderDark" style="padding: 4px 0;">
  <div class="spaceit">
    <div class="mb8" style="float: right; text-align: right;">
